item.title: Sproot Tips
item.description: Quicklinks Everyone Tanks DPS Healers Dungeons / Trials / Raids A few quick tips to help you when you load into a dungeon, trial, or raid. Everyone Stand in the Good Puddles! These will heal you and/or reduce damage taken! White Mage Scholar Astrologian Heals those in it Heals / mitigates damage Heals / Damage These do damage to enemies when they stand in it!
